<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“钉子。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把手伸进她的袋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“钉子！”她边说边递给他一个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸用锤子把它敲进木板里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“干得好！”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊和爸爸一上午都很忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把爷爷的木头搬到了有榆树的那个地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们在木场买了更多的木板和木桩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在地上放了两根柱子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为树屋的地板做了一个框架。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他结束时，他皱着眉头看着乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“搭档。”他说：“我们有个问题。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”乔伊惊讶地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看我们买的地板木头。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸指着12块木板说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们有两米半长。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看了看木板，然后抬头看了看爸爸做的框架。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她歪着头，眯起了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些木板看起来太长了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的眼力很好！”爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个框架有两米长，所以我们需要把每块木板缩短半米。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸和乔伊跪在一块木板旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把这个卷尺放在木板的末端。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸边说边把卷尺递给她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他沿着边缘拉长卷尺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是25厘米。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸又把卷尺拉长了一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是50厘米！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我用铅笔做记号。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸一边解释一边画了一条黑线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们就在这儿割板子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要测量并标记全部木板吗？”乔伊问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，我就把它们裁成合适的尺寸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，你知道吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们可以把剩下的木头送到回收中心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其他人也许能用得上。”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像我们用爷爷的木头一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了下午晚些时候，爸爸已经把树屋的地板钉在框架上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和乔伊坐在卡车的尾部，抬头看着他们的成果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接下来我们做什么？”乔伊问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们回收多余的木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还可以找到一些我们需要的东西。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们坐上卡车，朝山下公路开去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们到达中心时，乔伊跳下了车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她喜欢抬头看堆成山的碎纸板和破汽水罐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到了卡洛斯的爸爸——雷斯先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他负责整理所有的铜、锡、铁和钢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好，雷斯先生。”乔伊喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸和我在盖一座树屋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您有什么我们可以用的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，我们看看。”雷斯先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你需要桶吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可能需要。”乔伊回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在看一个纸板箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有一些旧钩子。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们可以把东西挂在上面。”雷斯先生说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把钩子扔进了她的桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”乔伊问道，“轮子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一种特殊的轮子。”雷斯先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它叫做滑轮。你可以用它和绳子把东西拉起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊转向爸爸。“我们需要一个吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿上它。”他说，“我们可以用它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这根杆子我们也拿着吧。”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这可能用得着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在墙边找到了一些铁板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的树屋屋顶！”乔伊大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那并不是全部。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还发现了一个小窗框和一扇旧门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把所有东西都堆在卡车后面，然后开车回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>